name: The Gatekeepers Project
description: The Gatekeeper Experiment: Does more exposure equal more sales? New nft artist do not have equitable access to exposure.  I will use my platforms (@nftmansa & @nftcolumn) to promote random nft artists by retweeting 100k random nfts. I anticipate an increase in sales given more exposure to a targeted audience.  Income will be measured by sales after retweet  notoriety will be measured by twitter engagement and following increases after retweet.  Each resell will generate another 100k retweets.
